    "description": "<div>Hi, opening up a discussion task for the client feedback on the site:&nbsp;<br><br>\n</div><div>\n<em style=\"color: rgb(185, 94, 6);\">One thing we need to address quickly for Lifetime is how the site only talks about Baton Rouge other than the addresses in the footer and specific service area pages. &nbsp; The home page, for example, only has Baton Rouge so anyone that gets there has no clue that we are a Houston company.&nbsp; We've setup GBP and some other referral sources to drive users to this page (</em><a href=\"https://lifetimero2stg.wpenginepowered.com/service-area/houston-tx/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><em style=\"color: rgb(185, 94, 6);\">https://lifetimero2stg.wpenginepowered.com/service-area/houston-tx/</em></a><em style=\"color: rgb(185, 94, 6);\">), but that's only for some users.</em>\n</div><div><br></div><div><em style=\"color: rgb(185, 94, 6);\">We have this scenario with our other sites as well but very prevalent with Lifetime.</em></div><div>\n<br><bc-attachment sgid=\"BAh7BkkiC19yYWlscwY6BkVUewdJIglkYXRhBjsAVEkiLmdpZDovL2JjMy9BdHRhY2htZW50LzgzNDQ1OTAxMj9leHBpcmVzX2luBjsAVEkiCHB1cgY7AFRJIg9hdHRhY2hhYmxlBjsAVA==--9e5bcbc5dc81c2ce3fd92f4ece5f8169157c1252\" content-type=\"image/png\" url=\"https://preview.3.basecamp.com/4226914/blobs/8b6f4e20-3370-11f1-8e22-0242ac120002/previews/full\" href=\"https://storage.3.basecamp.com/4226914/blobs/8b6f4e20-3370-11f1-8e22-0242ac120002/download/image.png\" filename=\"image.png\" filesize=\"35331\" width=\"881\" height=\"200\" previewable=\"true\" presentation=\"gallery\"><figure>\n    <img srcset=\"https://preview.3.basecamp.com/4226914/blobs/8b6f4e20-3370-11f1-8e22-0242ac120002/previews/full?dppx=2 2x, https://preview.3.basecamp.com/4226914/blobs/8b6f4e20-3370-11f1-8e22-0242ac120002/previews/full?dppx=1 1x, https://preview.3.basecamp.com/4226914/blobs/8b6f4e20-3370-11f1-8e22-0242ac120002/previews/full?dppx=3 3x, https://preview.3.basecamp.com/4226914/blobs/8b6f4e20-3370-11